    "The Frost Serpent emerged from the ice with a sound like cracking glaciers. It was massive, easily fifty feet long, with scales that shimmered like diamonds in the pale light. Its eyes were ancient and cold, and when it looked at me, I felt the weight of centuries of accumulated malice. This wasn't just a monster. This was a guardian, something that had been placed here to protect something important.",
